{"title":"Apple Script","date":"2018-08-09T16:00:00.000Z","author":"luoyayu","excerpt":"","slug":"2018-08-10-appleScript","comments":true,"tags":["Scripts"],"categories":["工具","macOS"],"updated":"2018-08-19T01:49:46.000Z","content":"<p>刚入手macOS时捣鼓的几个小脚本。直到今天发现Hexo的高亮如此辣眼睛，遂想到了Word可以导出html, 再结合Clion的富文本于是做出了html嵌入呈现代码的设计，写了个自动化脚本，自动把第一行注释内容作为文件名，通过clion导出html, 复制到博客路径下。<br>调用方法:<br><code>&lt;iframe id=&quot;iFrame0&quot; name=&quot;iFrame0&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot; onload=&quot;this.height=iFrame0.document.body.scrollHeight&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;/htmlcode/cf/cf1017c.html&quot; scrolling=&quot;no&quot; allowtransparency=&quot;yes&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</code><br>该调用实现了高度自适应, 注意同一博文中id的分配, 以及<code>/</code>指向<code>public/</code>, <code>HTML</code>资源文件存放在<code>themes/xxx/source/</code>下, 配合macOS的文本替换食用</p>\n<h1 id=\"预备\"><a href=\"#预备\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"预备\"></a>预备</h1><h2 id=\"Apple-按键对应的ANSI\"><a href=\"#Apple-按键对应的ANSI\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Apple 按键对应的ANSI\"></a>Apple 按键对应的ANSI</h2><details><div>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br